Bank of America Corporation Declares Quarterly Dividends
Wednesday, 11 Jan 2012 01:55pm EST
Bank of America Corporation announced that the Board of Directors declared a regular quarterly cash dividend on Bank of America common stock of $0.01 per share, payable on March 23, 2012 to shareholders of record as of March 2, 2012. The board also declared a regular quarterly cash dividend of $1.75 per share on the 7% Cumulative Redeemable Preferred Stock, Series B. The dividend is payable on April 25, 2012 to shareholders of record as of April 11, 2012.Â 
